<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="525" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="6.[97,1307,296,806]" pageId="6" pageNumber="525">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[100,437,690,723]" pageId="6" pageNumber="525">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. There are no major known threats to the Masked Ring-tailed Possum, but local people huntit for food.
</paragraph>
